cs.MM, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG

This paper is about emotion recognition using multimodal fusion techniques, which involves analyzing language, visual, and acoustic modalities. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia), which deals with the processing and analysis of multimedia data. The paper also involves natural language processing (NLP) and speech processing, which are subfields of cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.SD (Sound), respectively. Additionally, the paper uses computer vision techniques to analyze visual modalities, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also involves artificial intelligence techniques, such as Bayesian ranking algorithms, which are part of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
